{"tid":2173403,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"農夫山泉=中國可口可樂，你真係唔抽？","createTime":"2020-08-25T08:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T08:59:45.000Z","uid":43785,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8b528766a99ec8e8e39a15bd582c44534dd51fa2","tid":2173403,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"港股新手必看：農夫山泉終開閘，四大亮點看清這只現金奶牛！<br />\n<br />\n2020年是中國企業的IPO大年。寶新精選了二十二個(目前)市傳即將來港上市之新股進行優惠，率先迎來的是農夫山泉！<br />\n<br />\n　　農夫山泉這杯水也等太久了吧！終於定好在8月25日至28日招股，股市編號為09633，招股價在19.5至21.5港元，每手200股，入場費約4343元，並將於9月8日正式在港交所主板掛牌上市。中金公司和摩根士丹利擔任農夫山泉上市的聯席保薦人。農夫山泉按19.5元發行價計算，若發售完成而未行使超額配股權，股份市值2181.71億元。若按21.5元計算，發行完成而未行使超額配股權，股份市值2405.47億元。以2019年的市盈率（PE）計，為44至48倍。<br />\n<br />\n　　現時在港上市的軟飲料股份，中國旺旺(00151)市盈率16.5倍，康師傅(00322|)市盈率20.4倍，蒙牛(02319)市盈率30.3倍，維他奶(00345)市盈率54.8倍。<br />\n<br />\n　　股本方面，農夫山泉在發售完成後，內資股為62.118億股，佔總發行股份111.88億股的55.5%；由內資股轉換的H股佔45.882億股或41%；全球發行的H股為3.88億股，佔3.47%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/08/25/154905_3866272b7cd271f35b67c7f71a7d5e6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F08%2F25%2F154905_3866272b7cd271f35b67c7f71a7d5e6d.jpg&h=bcea2f98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基於農夫山泉的龍頭稀有性，可惜，所有人都能看到的機會就不是機會。農夫山泉還未正式開始招股，不少客戶已經提早預留了孖展額！目測將會有50萬+投資者參與農夫山泉打新盛宴。一手中籤率預計3-8%。200手+穩中一手。按乙組頭中籤率0.8%估算。600萬的資金預計只能拿到價值4.8萬的貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ZwAbRaYPMQan4fFV7mZPYw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2FZwAbRaYPMQan4fFV7mZPYw&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=ad8de450\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ZwAbRaYPMQan4fFV7mZPYw</a><br />\n好撚長，唔貼了，自己睇下四大亮點。<br />\n好多嘢香港網站都冇提到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n50倍PE支拿飲尿股，你地抽唔抽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一日都孖到爆晒，穩賺喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地係咪喺同錢鬥氣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你冇錢點同中共打呀？<br />\n買軍火，食黃店，都要錢啦"},{"pid":"a836925041625c03ab16c3081460d33537478679","tid":2173403,"uid":45498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"你點抽的"},{"pid":"d33d7ace69fee04f9f4dadab7fb869e59473da54","tid":2173403,"uid":256181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"好"},{"pid":"6c1dabe25121f11bbad95209beeded0984f59732","tid":2173403,"uid":101507,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:16:50.000Z","msg":"你點抽的"},{"pid":"9104b8dca62333f8131bb555015717048027d099","tid":2173403,"uid":167721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"你點抽的？"},{"pid":"c06cc29373f864d3ace8e58c056b339fb550f24a","tid":2173403,"uid":246731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:16:53.000Z","msg":"yes sir"},{"pid":"871935555170449fdb7874628c096db40fb301da","tid":2173403,"uid":261505,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T08:16:55.000Z","msg":"Yes Sir !<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9WVRM4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9WVRM4c.png&h=ec331784&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RUnkBNd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRUnkBNd.png&h=90cb38b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OxTuVp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OxTuVp.jpg&h=2a6085f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPJaEwL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPJaEwL.png&h=08788276&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAOgdKf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAOgdKf.png&h=f53d1a95&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https